#Mid-range combat: 16-25 tiles # Carbines, Assault Rifles
#Long range combat: 25-45 tiles # LMGs, Artillery, Battle Rifles, Snipers (min snapRange: 35)
#Extra long range combat: 46-60 # Snipers
